description: Minified Bootstrap v3.3.5 JavaScript library, including core components like alerts, buttons, modals, tooltips, popovers, scrollspy, tabs, affix, and transition support. The file enforces dependency on jQuery and includes transition and event handling logic for Bootstrap UI components.

methods.name: emulateTransitionEnd
methods.description: Simulates end of CSS transition for a given element after a specified duration.

methods.name: alert
methods.description: Handles alert component behaviors like dismissing alerts.

methods.name: button
methods.description: Enables toggle states and loading states for buttons.

methods.name: carousel
methods.description: Controls image/content carousels with cycling and slide transition functionalities.

methods.name: collapse
methods.description: Manages expand/collapse toggle for collapsible elements.

methods.name: dropdown
methods.description: Handles dropdown menu toggling and keyboard navigation.

methods.name: modal
methods.description: Controls modal dialog display, hiding, backdrop, and focus management.

methods.name: tooltip
methods.description: Provides tooltip display functionalities with positioning and show/hide controls.

methods.name: popover
methods.description: Provides popover UI component similar to tooltip with additional content support.

methods.name: scrollspy
methods.description: Automatically updates navigation based on scroll position.

methods.name: getPosition
methods.description: Calculates position of an element for tooltip/popover placement.
